    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AccessorioDidattica
    Represents the possible accessories available in an (AulaDidattica).
    AccessorioLaboratorio
    Represents the possible accessories available in a laboratory classroom (Laboratorio).
    Aula
    Represents an abstract classroom with basic properties such as number, capacity, and type.
    AulaAdapter
    Custom Gson adapter for deserializing JSON into AulaInterface.
    AulaDidattica
    Represents an AulaDidattica, extends Aula class and implementing AulaInterface.
    AulaInterface
    Defines the contract for Aula, specifying methods to access basic properties and accessories of a Aula.
    AulaInterface.TipoAula
    Represents the type of classroom, either a Laboratorio or a AulaDidattica.
    BookingRenderer
    Custom renderer for table cells, applying colors and borders based on booking data.
    FileManager
    Manages file operations for saving and loading Prenotazione objects.
    JsonUtils
    Provides utility methods for reading and writing JSON data related to Aula and Prenotazione.
    Laboratorio
    Represents a Laboratorio classroom, extends Aula class and implementing AulaInterface.
    LocalDateAdapter
    Custom Gson adapter for serializing and deserializing LocalDate to and from JSON file.
    LocalTimeAdapter
    Custom Gson adapter for serializing and deserializing LocalTime to and from a JSON file.
    Main
    The main class for the application.
    MainView
    GUI for managing classroom bookings.
    Prenotazione
    Represents a booking for a classroom, encapsulating details such as classroom number, date, time slot, booker's name, and booking motivation.
